Welcome to Claws Mail
---------------------

Now that you have set up your account you can fetch your
mail by clicking the 'Get Mail' button at the left of the
toolbar.

Claws Mail has lots of extra features accessible via plugins,
like anti-spam filtering and learning (via the Bogofilter or
SpamAssassin plugins), privacy protection (via PGP/Mime), an RSS
aggregator, a calendar, and much more. You can load them from
the menu entry '/Configuration/Plugins'.

You can change your Account Preferences by using the menu
entry '/Configuration/Preferences for current account'
and change the general Preferences by using
'/Configuration/Preferences'.

You can find further information in the Claws Mail manual,
which can be accessed by using the menu entry '/Help/Manual'
or online at the URL given below.

Useful URLs
-----------
Homepage:      <https://www.claws-mail.org/>
Manual:        <https://www.claws-mail.org/documentation.php>
FAQ:           <https://www.claws-mail.org/faq/index.php>
Themes:        <https://www.claws-mail.org/themes.php>
Mailing Lists: <https://www.claws-mail.org/MLs.php>

